Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:392826,394619}Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.28,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:394619,396287}Hey, hey! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.74,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:397330,398748}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:398748,401042}Great, now my stomach's grumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.92,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:401042,403920}If you're gonna grumble now,\NI'm soon gonna join…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:407549,410385}Yes. I was so surprised when he\Nsuddenly yelled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.51,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:410385,411511}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:411511,413179}Is he still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:56.76,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:413179,416766}I don't think he came here\Nto take singing lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:416766,418893}Is it so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.35,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:418893,421354}Nowadays about everyone\Nwould like to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:422856,423732}Kōda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:423732,424899}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.90,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:424899,426901}Do you have any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:426901,428028}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:11.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:428028,431322}This man wants to repair the damage\Nhe had caused to a certain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:432741,435326}He wants to clear\Na misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:435326,436828}To a certain girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:21.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:437829,441416}Tell me, how many of\Nyour friends would be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:441416,443251}to go that far for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:32.59,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:448923,452594}People who are endowed with\Nsuch kindness can become true singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:460351,461770}You're being mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:45.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:461770,465023}You make it sound like a rich person\Nsuch as myself cannot succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:465940,467525}It's not a matter of wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:467525,469527}It's about the spirit.\NThe heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:470320,474032}Stop judging others by\Nappearance alone, to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:478495,481498}Ishiguro Boxing Gym{NOTE:石黒ボクシングジム}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.28,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:478995,480288}You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.08,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:480288,482082}What were you doing, Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.20,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:482082,484209}I'm sorry.\NI'll get to it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:09.25,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:485835,489255}I don't mind if you work,\Nbut you'll end up badly if you overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.17,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:489255,491174}Hey, Fanni!\NAre you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.34,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:491174,492342}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:492342,493051}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.13,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:493051,494135}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:494135,496971}I'm here to see Fanni-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.68,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:496971,499682}Not gonna happen.\NHe's training for his match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.76,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:499682,500767}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:500767,502519}But it's only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:25.52,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:502519,505522}If you're his fan,\Nyou should respect his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:506439,507524}Please give this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.77,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:507524,508775}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:508775,510693}It's just a little\Ngood luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.65,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:511528,513655}Ah, I see. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:513655,515615}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.32,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:515615,517325}I'll make sure\Nthat he gets this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:518159,519160}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:520370,521871}Ah, Yumemaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.79,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:522747,524791}You won't like the news I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:524791,526292}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:50.50,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:526292,530505}Kuma-san went to talk\Nto Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:530505,532382}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.96,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:532382,535969}I tried to stop him,\Nbut he just didn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:535969,538429}You should've told me earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.63,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:538429,539639}Ah, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.18,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:547230,548189}Oh, it's Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.57,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:552193,555572}Is she the girl\NEgawa-sensei referred to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.69,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:555572,557699}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:564914,567041}Food… Food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:567041,567959}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:567959,571045}A-Ah… Nozomi-chan, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.71,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:571045,572714}Did you stay here all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:572714,575091}Kuma-san, why are you doing\Nsomething so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:35.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:575091,575800}Eh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:575800,577135}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:577135,580013}No! I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.47,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:580013,581472}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:581472,584767}Kuma-san, I appreciate your feelings.\NThat's why I'd like you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:584767,586227}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:589230,590773}Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.07,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:594277,596070}Come on in. We'll talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.03,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:602660,604037}So tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:608917,611336}You're lucky to be blessed\Nwith such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:612003,614005}Oh? Yes. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:614005,616883}You see, for me\Nthe music is something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:616883,620428}that comes from one's heart,\Nsimple and sincere like your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:620428,621512}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.26,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:621512,624265}Oh, man, that was great.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:625099,626100}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:626100,628978}Frankly, I'm a little bit jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:628978,630480}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:35.98,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:630480,635985}Mine-kun is surrounded by friends\Nthat can support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:39.57,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:635985,639572}If she's a person who can\Nappreciate having such friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.61,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:639572,640615}Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:44.03,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:640615,644035}Are you going to forgive her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:644035,645536}Yes, and I'm taking her\Nas a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.37,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:648623,651376}Right on! Great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:651376,652669}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.46,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:654295,655463}I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:655463,657173}Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.63,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:657173,658633}Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.46,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:658633,660468}– I'm gonna cry.\N– Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:660468,663304}It's all thanks to you, Kuma-san.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.76,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:663304,664764}There's one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.14,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:664764,666140}– Huh?\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:666849,668643}You'll have to pass\Nan admission test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:670270,670937}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.57,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:676985,679570}Congratulations,\Ncongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.66,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:684242,685660}I'm the happiest uncle on Earth.
Comment: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:35.95,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:695954,695954}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.91,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:708333,709917}I'm happy for you, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:53.00,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:709917,713004}Your mom is very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:713004,716966}But I feel kinda bad.\NI'm just doing what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.17,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:716966,719177}What are you talking about, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.92,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:719177,721929}Do you want to become\Na professional singer that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:721929,722972}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:07.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:722972,727185}To tell you the truth, I put\Nall of my hope in Egawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.31,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:727185,729312}Don't worry about anything\Naround the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:13.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:729312,733816}Think how happy your father would be\Nif he learned you're a star when he woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.81,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:733816,735818}Let's hope everything goes well\Nfor Dad's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:22.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:738821,742909}I know. I'll try to do my best,\Nno matter how hard it's going to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.16,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:742909,744160}That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.62,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:744160,747622}If you keep it up,\Neverything will be a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:747622,750500}{\i1}Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.46,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:751000,752460}I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:752460,753544}So she finally did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.17,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:753544,755171}Yes. She did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.21,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:755171,757215}I better win my match, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.50,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:757215,759509}I'll go and cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.76,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:762428,763763}I'm gonna win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.94,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:771437,773940}What on earth are you doing?\NNext is cleaning the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:54.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:773940,774732}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.99,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:783866,784992}Mine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.41,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:786119,787412}Next is the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:787412,788996}On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:792750,795712}If this keeps up,\NI'll forget how to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.98,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:818109,820987}Would you look at that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.57,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:820987,822572}She's just like you said, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:46.28,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:822572,826284}Where does she think she is?\NShe sings as if she were at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:826284,830037}That's why I wanted you\Nto talk to him, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:830037,831956}What is he thinking,\Nmaking her his student?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.87,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:831956,833875}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:835376,836252}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:06.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:840590,846554}She's not used to this job yet, so I'm going\Nto cut her some slack for time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.47,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:846554,849474}Your generosity\Nis outstanding, Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:13.51,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:849474,853519}but I only hope that she doesn't enjoy\Nlessons more accurate than Miki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:16.02,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:853519,856022}Are you talking about Mine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.10,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:856022,857106}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:22.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:858441,862111}I intend to make her work harder\Nthan your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:26.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:862111,866365}If she doesn't keep up, she'll get\Ndiscouraged and give up by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:29.11,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:866365,869118}I see. That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:869911,873122}But if in spite of everything she holds up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:36.62,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:873122,876626}it will mean that she really\Nhas a great artistic talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:40.54,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:877126,880546}Are you suggesting that\Nmy daughter doesn't have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:46.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:881714,886427}What I'd like to say is that if Miki\Nneeds to rely on other people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:886427,890264}and bring her mother to meetings like that,\Nthere's no point in the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:55.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:890264,895186}You can't enter the world of music\Nwith this attitude or you'll get crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.48,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:900817,903486}Alright, Miki-san.\NLet's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:903486,904445}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.16,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:908991,911160}Hurry up and finish the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:11.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:911160,911953}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:923840,925216}Have a nice day, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.46,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:925216,927468}Nozomi-san was your name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:927468,928803}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.09,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:928803,931097}It seems that you also take singing lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:37.14,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:931097,937144}But in your place, I would not be too ecstatic\Nso as not to disappoint my followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:937144,939397}E… Ecstatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:41.48,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:939397,941482}– Let's head home.\N– Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.69,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:941482,944694}Being raised around yakuza\Nmust've made you tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:944694,946696}Kōda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:49.65,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:946696,949657}But if these friends of yours knew\Nthat you work here as a servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:52.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:949657,952285}they would've come to save you\Nwith pitchforks and torches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:956956,958332}{\i1}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:01.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:958332,961836}{\i1}What would Kuma-san\Nand everyone think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:976559,977310}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:978311,981522}It's the middle of the night. Who gave you\Nthe permission to touch the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:981522,984108}I don't remember having\Naccepted you as my student yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:984108,985026}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:30.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:986193,990031}Playing the piano early in the morning,\Nsinging here and there during chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:990031,993117}Do you really think\Nyou can become a singer like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:993117,994243}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:995912,997538}It wasn't my intention\Nto disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:998164,1000708}Not yet. Not yet. Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:45.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000708,1005129}I've only began to test\Nthe limits of your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005129,1008341}If you really can't stand it,\Nthen waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.67,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008341,1010676}I don't need you.\NGo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011719,1013721}What do you think music is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015389,1018142}Music is nothing\Nlike mathematics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.60,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018142,1021604}It must be something that comes out\Nnaturally from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021604,1023189}Take a look, Mine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027026,1028861}A canary…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.28,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028861,1031280}It's true, these birds\Nhave a beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031280,1035409}But they can not move\Nanyone's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.74,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035409,1037745}That's because they sing\Nwith their throats alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:21.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038829,1041290}But humans…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041290,1045127}are capable of singing\Nfrom the bottom of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045127,1046837}You have to be passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.63,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046837,1049632}But look at yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049632,1052176}You're not even sure\Nwhat the future holds for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052176,1056180}You're so naive.\NThere's no room for naivety in music!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056180,1058516}But I'll do my best—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:39.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058516,1059642}Spare me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:46.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063062,1066607}{\i1}Nozomi became lost in thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066607,1068651}{\i1}"I'm just like that canary."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068651,1070736}{\i1}"A canary."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:56.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070736,1076117}{\i1}"Even if I have nice voice,\NI can't sing well."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:18:01.20,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076117,1081205}{\i1}"Yes. I didn't know\Nhow to sing until now."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:19.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094385,1099557}{\i1}Humans are capable of singing\Nfrom the bottom of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103102,1105021}{\i1}I'm like that canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105855,1107064}{\i1}If I want to sing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108107,1109442}{\i1}If I want to sing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110609,1111902}{\i1}To sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111902,1113446}{\i1}If I want to sing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113446,1114905}Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114905,1116449}Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116449,1117783}Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117783,1119410}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119410,1122246}Please teach me what music is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:48.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122663,1128627}{\i1}The first thing Egawa Isao had taught\Nto Nozomi wasn't how to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:52.29,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128627,1132298}{\i1}It was about the nature of music.\NThat it's all about passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.01,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135051,1138012}So many people came\Nto cheer for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.38,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138012,1139388}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.64,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139388,1142641}We just oughta show to her\Nthat she's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:07.52,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142641,1147521}Yeah. Once in a while it won't hurt to show\Nour faces to Nozomi and encourage her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:11.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147521,1151817}She works very hard, but she has\Nto know how much we support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:19.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158991,1159950}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163704,1164830}Kuma-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164830,1166123}Yumemaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166123,1168751}Tatsu-san…\NEven the greengrocer man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174048,1175007}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184183,1187895}So if I understand correctly, you're here\Nto attend a lesson with Nozomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.48,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187895,1191482}Yes, this is the only thing we can do\Nfor her as her fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:55.82,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191482,1195820}We thought to at least encourage\Nher a little. You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198572,1200241}Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.74,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200241,1203744}Oh? W-Why is my niece\Nwearing such dirty clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203744,1205704}What's wrong with her clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:09.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205704,1209250}She's here to take\Nlessons from you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:13.62,Default,Tatsu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209250,1213629}Exactly. You promised to take her\Nas a student, not as a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213629,1215673}H-Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215673,1216590}Kuma-san, Tatsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.84,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216590,1218843}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218843,1220427}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:25.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220427,1225808}Sensei taught me about\Nthe meaning of music yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:31.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225808,1231021}I have realized how I had been\Nthinking only about myself I was singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231021,1233732}See? That's why it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233732,1235234}Just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:39.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235234,1239029}He's going to teach me,\Nbut it's not going to happen overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239029,1242700}I'll work hard so that\NI can take proper lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242700,1244785}Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:47.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244785,1247705}If you want to cheer\Nfor Nozomi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247705,1251500}please accept and encourage\Nher as she is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:55.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251500,1255254}Through the hard work she does now,\Nher talent is going to flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.71,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255254,1257715}Heh, Nozomi-chan's talent, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.59,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257715,1261594}Right. That means she's going to make songs\Nas beautiful as the one she's composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263095,1264597}Yeah. I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.76,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265389,1266765}You've composed a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:10.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266765,1270019}Yes. It was a school assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:13.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270019,1273272}Would you like to sing it?\NYour whole fanclub is here for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.85,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273272,1274857}Do you want to hear her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.35,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274857,1276358}Yeah! Sing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.23,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276358,1278235}We wanna hear Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.07,Default,Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278235,1280070}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:34.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284992,1294585}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Music is your friend  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:43.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294585,1303010}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When things get sad, it stays with you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:52.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303010,1312811}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  You and I hold hands together  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:22:01.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312811,1321237}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The song of hope belongs to everyone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:10.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321237,1330329}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Everyone's song fills the sky  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:19.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330329,1339296}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's believe in the tomorrow  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that will spread someday  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:32.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339296,1352351}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's believe in the tomorrow  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that will spread someday  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.60,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353060,1355604}– Good bye!\N– See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355604,1357106}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357106,1358357}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.31,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358774,1361318}{\i1}Certainly, this girl has the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:43.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361318,1363529}{\i1}With a little practice,\Nmaybe… who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364780,1366657}{\i1}Well then, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:52.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366657,1372621}{\i1}You may be a weak canary now,\Nbut some day you'll soar in the skies.
Comment: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:55.63,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1375633,1375633}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:04.50,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377493,1384500}{\i1}Nozomi's teenage heart gets filled\Nmore and more with thoughts of Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:09.21,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384500,1389213}{\i1}Fanni also feels attracted\Nby Nozomi's brightness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.30,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389213,1393300}{\i1}Nozomi returns exhilarated\Nfrom another meeting with Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:17.22,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393300,1397221}{\i1}But to her surprise, she gets\Nscolded by Egawa again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:22.05,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397221,1402059}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"The Promise Between The Two"
